1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
("The Unique Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 17=

4
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:53,760
Got it.

5
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:55,760
Okay.

6
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:57,000
No problem.

7
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:58,280
I'll be in touch.

8
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:08,760
Hello.

9
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,000
May I ask who you are?

10
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,200
Dr. Chen,

11
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:12,840
right?

12
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:15,400
My sister, Xiaomi,

13
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,520
has been troubling you
quite a bit lately.

14
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:24,560
So,

15
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,000
you're Miss Qiao's brother.

16
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,360
Xiaomi is my patient.

17
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,960
I wouldn't call it trouble.

18
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:31,440
Dr. Chen,

19
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:33,280
let's not beat around the bush.

20
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,400
When you treat Xiaomi from now on,

21
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,040
pay a little more attention.

22
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,840
But not too much attention.

23
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,400
I'm afraid

24
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,280
I don't understand.

25
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,240
That's okay.

26
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:46,800
You'll understand eventually.

27
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,200
Look, Mr. Qiao.

28
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,800
I'm just a regular psychologist.

29
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,040
I'm afraid

30
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,120
there's not much I can do for you.

31
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:59,280
If I say you can help,

32
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,160
then you can help.

33
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:05,160
Otherwise, you and your clinic...

34
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,800
Mr. Qiao,

35
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,640
my consultation fee

36
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:18,600
is very expensive.

37
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,120
Money isn't an issue.

38
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,080
Deal.

39
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,920
That's more like it.

40
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:30,000
I'll be in touch.

41
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:34,360
(He's really afraid of
Qiao Xiaomi regaining her memory.)

42
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,000
(Could it be)

43
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,680
(there's another reason?)

44
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:41,280
(This is getting more interesting.)

45
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,560
Tell me, when people die,

46
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,960
do they go somewhere else,

47
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,680
or do they disappear completely?

48
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,520
There's a saying.

49
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,240
As long as someone

50
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:58,120
still remembers her,

51
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,680
she never truly disappears.

52
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:02,760
(Xiaoduo.)

53
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,080
(I'm sorry.)

54
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,600
(Even though I'll never forget you,)

55
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:09,120
(I can't keep living
in the past anymore.)

56
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:12,840
(Ji Ran.)

57
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,680
(I've realized that Xiaomi)

58
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,720
(is completely different
from what I imagined.)

59
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,360
(She's kind and resilient.)

60
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:22,240
(I should've told her
why I approached her.)

61
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,240
(But now I finally understand)

62
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,640
(the helplessness you felt
when the words wouldn't come.)

63
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,160
(I'm sorry.)

64
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,880
(I'll do my best
to help Xiaomi remember her past.)

65
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:34,640
(Then let her)

66
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:37,240
(make her own choice between us.)

67
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,360
Are you okay?

68
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,320
I'm fine.

69
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,640
Shouldn't we go paint again today?

70
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:32,200
Otherwise I'll forget everything
I learned last time.

71
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,760
I'm a little busy with work today.

72
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:36,000
Have Xiaoyi go with you.

73
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:42,280
Qin Yu, if you want
to quit, just say it.

74
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,640
Do I look like I want to quit?

75
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,080
I really have things to do.

76
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,480
What could possibly be
more important than me?

77
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:08,200
Come on.

78
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:09,400
Let's do something simple today.

79
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:15,160
Crayons?

80
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,680
Aren't those for little kids?

81
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,680
Little kid.

82
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:26,320
Just draw whatever you want first.

83
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,160
Get a feel for it.

84
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,960
You don't really think
I can't draw, do you?

85
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,240
I...

86
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:39,440
Fine.

87
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,200
Don't come over.

88
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,080
Stand still.

89
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,160
Face left.

90
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,520
Now right.

91
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,760
A little forward.

92
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:09,840
Well.

93
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,680
Back a little.

94
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:11,680
You...

95
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,680
Hurry up.

96
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:20,040
Do you even know how to smile?

97
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:31,360
Wait.

98
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:32,840
It's done?

99
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:44,000
Looking at it now,

100
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:48,800
there are actually
a lot of nice touches in it.

101
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,760
Two months is far too short.

102
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,640
What if, when the time comes,

103
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,960
I can't keep my promise?

104
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,960
Will you kick me out?

105
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,800
Back when you wanted to leave,

106
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:10,000
did I try to stop you?

107
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,960
You got on your knees
and begged me in tears.

108
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,040
Just kidding.

109
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:22,800
You told me to get lost.

110
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,160
If you

111
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,880
still want to leave this time,

112
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,760
I won't stop you either.

113
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:41,200
But,

114
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:43,920
if you want to stay,

115
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,640
I'll be very happy.

116
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:49,640
Really happy.

117
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,560
Mr. Qin is going
to Man Tea Garden tomorrow

118
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:17,360
for an art event
hosted by the City Art Association.

119
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,960
Why don't you go with him
and get some fresh air?

120
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,360
I'm swamped with work.

121
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,280
How do I have time for that?

122
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,880
You two used to love going there.

123
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,920
Maybe if you go,

124
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,760
you'll remember some good times.

125
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,280
Then I'll ask him about it later.

126
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,120
I already brought it up to him.

127
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,400
He didn't object.

128
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:37,720
He said he'll pick you up
tomorrow morning.

129
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:41,840
He told you that?

130
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,800
Yeah.

131
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,040
Then why didn't he tell me himself?

132
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:46,840
Then go ask him.

133
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,520
Not working today?

134
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,160
Don't you still have
a meeting this afternoon?

135
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:14,120
I've already gone through everything
with Xiaoyi.

136
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,040
Just thinking about
going to the tea garden tomorrow,

137
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:18,280
I'm already too excited to focus.

138
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:20,920
Are you a little kid?

139
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,720
How about we leave right now?

140
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,080
I can't wait anymore.

141
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,480
I haven't even packed yet.

142
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:26,920
Besides,

143
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:29,000
we're only staying
in the countryside for two days.

144
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,440
Why are you so excited?

145
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:31,600
Because

146
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,160
we've never gone together before.

147
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:35,720
By the way,

148
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,880
did we ever travel together before?

149
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,440
Of course we did.

150
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:44,000
Then we must've gone to a lot of places.

151
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:47,120
So,

152
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,840
which place do you
remember the most?

153
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:56,040
Every place I went with you
meant something to me.

154
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:00,120
Then we must've taken
a lot of photos, right?

155
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:02,720
We did.

156
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,200
I want to see them.

157
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,120
Just give me a little time.

158
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,000
Let me sort through them.

159
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,000
I want to pick out your best photos.

160
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,440
I want to see them now.

161
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:20,920
Come on.

162
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,200
I'm going to pack first.

163
00:10:29,880 --> 00:10:31,080
(If you won't show me,)

164
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,600
(then I'll find them myself.)

165
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,280
Xiaoduo,

166
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,440
I like you.

167
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,440
Not even the King of Hell

168
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,080
could break a promise like this.

169
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,840
You dummy.

170
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,280
(Who exactly)

171
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,400
(is this person?)

172
00:11:47,627 --> 00:11:49,697
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

173
00:11:49,697 --> 00:11:53,117
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

174
00:11:54,717 --> 00:11:56,607
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

175
00:11:56,607 --> 00:12:00,597
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

176
00:12:01,837 --> 00:12:03,697
♪Let me go, set me free♪

177
00:12:03,697 --> 00:12:07,737
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

178
00:12:08,277 --> 00:12:13,687
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

179
00:12:15,037 --> 00:12:17,177
♪The freedom you gave me♪

180
00:12:17,177 --> 00:12:20,817
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

181
00:12:22,077 --> 00:12:24,347
♪Love can barely move forward♪

182
00:12:24,347 --> 00:12:28,127
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

183
00:12:29,227 --> 00:12:31,467
♪The closeness I long for♪

184
00:12:31,467 --> 00:12:35,857
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

185
00:12:36,267 --> 00:12:38,087
♪I don't want to break free♪

186
00:12:38,087 --> 00:12:43,457
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪
